Premier Oscar Mabuyane has given a breakdown of the 21 Covid-19 confirmed cases in the Eastern Cape. The update is as follows: Nelson Mandela Bay Metro has 11 cases followed by Buffalo City Metro with 4 and Sarah Baartman District with 4. Amathole District has 1 and Chris Hani District also stands at 1. Meanwhile, the USA today went over 300 thousand confirmed Covid-19 cases, while Italy and Spain each have 124 thousand cases. As of Friday evening there were just short of1.18 million confirmed Covid-19 cases globally, with almost 63 thousand dead. In the public interest, none of our corona virus news coverage will be placed behind our paywall and will be available free for all to read. If you would like to support our mission of delivering award-winning, independent local news, please consider taking out a subscription by clicking here.